S3 Storage Optimization

S3 Intelligent Tiering:
  auto moves objects
  between storage classes
  based on access patterns ✅

Storage classes cost:
  Standard          → $0.023/GB  (frequent access)
  Infrequent Access → $0.0125/GB (save 45%) ✅
  Glacier           → $0.004/GB  (save 83%) ✅
  Glacier Deep      → $0.00099/GB(save 96%) ✅

Lifecycle policies:
  files older than 30 days → IA ✅
  files older than 90 days → Glacier ✅
  auto delete after 365 days ✅
